  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for dracut",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for dracut fixes the following issue\n\n- CVE-2026-6893: Root code execution via DHCP options command injection (bsc#1268322).\n\nChanges for dracut:\n\n- Update to version 055+suse.365.g79144c5:\n * fix(network-legacy): sanitize DHCP values in dhclient-script.sh (bsc#1268322, CVE-2026-6893)\n * fix(network-legacy): add input validation to RFC 3442 route parser\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
